00:34:17.061 --> 00:34:19.626
slow down.
If I throw it up slower than

00:34:19.626 --> 00:34:22.970
the escape velocity,
then it's going to rise to some

00:34:22.970 --> 00:34:25.790
height, stop,
turn around and fall back.

00:34:25.790 --> 00:34:29.257
Right?
So, that's what happens with an

00:34:29.257 --> 00:34:31.110
