has to lose energy as it moves

00:35:25.588 --> 00:35:30.083
away from the Earth.
But light, as we know,

00:35:30.083 --> 00:35:32.750
always travels at the speed of
light.

00:35:32.750 --> 00:35:35.820
It doesn't slow down.
It can't slow down.

00:35:35.820 --> 00:35:38.912
So, what it has to do is,
